==Hungarian==
===Etymology===
From the same Finno-Ugric root *''wetä'' as Finnish [[vetää]]
===Verb===
'''vezet''' (''infinitive:'' [[vezetni]])

#to [[lead]], to lead to
#:Ez az [[ajtó]] vezet... &mdash; ''This door leads to...''
#to [[drive]]
#:[[tud|Tud]] [[kocsi|kocsit]] vezetni? &mdash; ''Can you drive a car?''

